             was indicted for <rs id="t18000402-42-off232" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18000402-42-off232" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000402-42-off232" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18000402-42-cd233" type="crimeDate">20th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000402-42-off232 t18000402-42-cd233"></join>, five pounds of mutton, value 2s. 6d.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18000402-42-victim347" type="victimName">
                  William 
                  Lane
               <interp inst="t18000402-42-victim347" type="surname" value="Lane"></interp>
